INSERT INTO native_trigger (
            external_id,
            workspace_id,
            service_name,
            script_path,
            is_flow,
            webhook_token_prefix,
            service_config
        ) VALUES (
            $1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7
        )
        ON CONFLICT (external_id, workspace_id, service_name)
        DO UPDATE SET script_path = $4, is_flow = $5, webhook_token_prefix = $6, service_config = $7, error = NULL, updated_at = NOW()
